metadata.name: The Sisters of Mercy
metadata.description:
AI creation using Stable Diffusion script within Visions of Chaos software.

Generated by giving maximum licence to the AI to come up with its own interpretation of generic prompts.  "Exquisitely detailed digital art" was the theme and "By everyman" was the only style guidance.

And the title? A doffing of the cap to one of the greatest songwriters ever, my dear departed Leonard Cohen.
